reviewText: This is the TV show I will write and produce new episodes of at Nelvana showing how they got the button out of the storm drain and put the button back on Corduroy The Bear's overalls and that Corduroy The Bear does have two buttons on his overalls this year and forever. In those new episodes I will write and produce at Nelvana the animation will stay the same but it will have new added features to the show such as McDonald's and other cool stuff from real life and new characters too and also that Corduroy The Bear permanently had two buttons on his overalls.
